dct_description_sm: Relief shown by gradient tints and spot heights. Directory, tourist information, and B & W ancillary map ("Mytilēnē = Mytilini") on verso. Includes text and inset view ("Astka megara tēs Mytilēnēs = bourgeois mansions of Mytilini"). Tourist map with roads emphasized. Panel title. Tourist information on verso
